==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: bú huàn guă ér huàn bù jūn
===Proverb===
'''[[不]][[患]][[寡]][[而]][[患]][[不]][[均]]'''
# (of money, wealth etc) Do not worry if there is not enough to go around, only worry if it is not evenly distributeed (among the people).
